Existem lagartas que se parecem com raminhos de plantas<question-record><question></question><answer><text>.</text><feedback></feedback><correct>1</correct></answer><clue></clue></question-record> E h&amp;#x00e1; grilos que imitam folhas<question-record><question></question><answer><text>.</text><feedback></feedback><correct>1</correct></answer><clue></clue></question-record> Muitos animais ficam com a cor e a forma dos lugares em que est&amp;#x00e3;o<question-record><question></question><answer><text>.</text><feedback></feedback><correct>1</correct></answer><clue></clue></question-record> Eles fazem isso para se defender dos inimigos ou capturar outros bichos que servem de alimento. Esses truques s&amp;#x00e3;o chamados de mimetismo<question-record><question></question><answer><text>,</text><feedback></feedback><correct>1</correct></answer><clue></clue></question-record> isto &amp;#x00e9;<question-record><question></question><answer><text>,</text><feedback></feedback><correct>1</correct></answer><clue></clue></question-record> imita&amp;#x00e7;&amp;#x00e3;o<question-record><question></question><answer><text>.</text><feedback></feedback><correct>1</correct></answer><clue></clue></question-record>

